  "detailed_description": "<strong>Sneak-Sample-Morph-Fight-Hinder-Rescue-Hide-Escape.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869090/extras/d60a78583701dafb97ee7ee5f79eceaa.webp?t=1535489786\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <strong>Sneak/Fight</strong> your way through procedurally generated outposts/arenas to rescue the lost.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869090/extras/ffbe9e556cc5ac0f21d0f8b239d0e5b3.webp?t=1535489786\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <strong>Sample</strong> others to gain the temporary ability to morph into them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869090/extras/c10c6ea8534e92489cb85266efda53fc.webp?t=1535489786\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <strong>Hinder</strong> your immortal opponents revival by rolling their 'Eye' away.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869090/extras/1e44439bbd7defc17982b18b4d7ee67c.webp?t=1535489786\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <strong>Hide</strong> and dodge enemies by using the interactable/destructible environment to your advantage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869090/extras/cb75e996c173e384260840ffab4b954a.webp?t=1535489786\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <strong>Escape.</strong><br><br><strong><u>FEATURES:</u></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869090/extras/8e52999f882c4ff8b8873d524e4045e5.webp?t=1535489786\" width=16 height=16 /></span> A bunch of beings to sample, fight, and eavesdrop on.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869090/extras/33535188f385f04d2f66561e89d10cfa.webp?t=1535489786\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Infinite procedural outposts and arenas, each with their own unique setups.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869090/extras/cd69c04b0dfae9356a1de094794787d2.webp?t=1535489786\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Local co-op gameplay, plug in a controller and sample and save as a duo.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869090/extras/8791af2810129cfdd32b4e112e6c06fd.webp?t=1535489786\" width=16 height=16 /></span> A dozen wonderful characters to unlock, each with their own challenge and skill.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869090/extras/9a009ff5b4a1150d5a658e04d0c6b029.webp?t=1535489786\" width=16 height=16 /></span> A variety of infusers, useful as temporary boosts or wells to pull a sample out of.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869090/extras/21c0a78bc935a3501734291ff10f6a29.webp?t=1535489786\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Fluctuating, but ever increasing, difficulty with an absorbing blend of stealth and action.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869090/extras/58e175c68ae3e1aec8255d7249a91578.webp?t=1535489786\" width=16 height=16 /></span> A story that sneaks up on you.",
